'''Tishwii''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] of plant that was originally native to the [[Yuuzhan Vong galaxy]]. Grown by [[Shaper caste|shapers]], its leaves were burned by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] during sacrificial ceremonies.

